{
  "stem": "13469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we picked it all up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and by the time we finished, we knew a lot about Judaism.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we never really [LAUGHS] remember having been taught it properly, probably-- properly, anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just remember that Naarden was yet another good place for sports.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, and-- [LAUGHTER] --there, [LAUGHS] all my life seemed to revolve about going to school, which I again did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we again have reports from the days that I went to school there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I got good marks, even in Dutch, from this school in Naarden.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- but there, I remember playing lots of football, in particular.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I played not just for the school team.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I played for a local town team there and remember some of the events there and scoring goals and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I also remember the ice skating again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Naarden was an ideal place for ice skating because it had this moat all the way around, this fortress.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So that froze in the winter that we were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it was an ideal place for skating around and playing ice hockey and all sorts of things like that-- really great.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had a big swimming-- there were swimming baths, of course, everywhere in Heemstede.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't mention that we had several swimming baths where we went regularly, all the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we spent all our time not swimming, really, but diving in and climbing out and diving in again and playing tag and being a nuisance kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In Haarlem, I remember playing football in the swimming bowl-- in the swimming pool, which you were not supposed to kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I fell through a great, big, glass panel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I had a big cut in my arm.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
